Milrinone was originally synthesized at the Sterling Winthrop Research Institute in the 1980s.[A228333] It was approved by the FDA on December 31, 1987, and was marketed under the trademark PRIMACOR® by Sanofi-Aventis US before being discontinued.[L31483]', '["C01CE02"]', '[]');
